title: Rep. John Katko, Stimulus, Covid-19 Strain

description:
Guests: Nancy Cook, Bloomberg White House reporter, Kriti Gupta, Bloomberg markets live reporter, Max Burns, Democratic Strategist, Scott Tranter, CEO of 0ptimus and former Data Science Director for Marco Rubio for President, and Rep.
